    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="chu">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_03618/">ка<unclear>м</unclear>ень</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_08903/">стльпь</w> <w lemma="граматкъ">гра  
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>матка</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/evtdict/evt_show/d_04266">прѣста
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>в</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_08538">сѧ</w> <persName ref="names.xml#n003">ѣ<space quantity="2" unit="character"/>нь</persName> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_00647/"><expan><abbr>б</abbr><ex>ог</ex><abbr>ь</abbr></expan></w>
                    <lb n="4"/> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_01998/">да</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_02994/">го</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_06815/">пом<space quantity="2" unit="character"/>ене</w>  
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <head xml:lang="bg"></head>
                    <head xml:lang="en"></head>
                        <app loc=""><note></note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <seg xml:lang="bg"> 
                    Каменен стълб на гра-
                    матика. Предста-
                    ви се Ян. Бог
                    да го помене!
                </seg>
                <seg xml:lang="en"> 
                    A stone pillar of a gram-
                    marian. Jan presen-
                    ted himself. May God 
                    remember him!
                </seg>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>
                    <seg xml:lang="bg"><note>„Блокът е преизползван поне два пъти – за поменателен знак и в строежа на църквата“ (Хаджиев 2003:225). На редове 3 и 4 в камъка се вижда издълбана малка ямка с неясно предназначение.</note></seg>
                    <seg xml:lang="en"><note>„The block was reused at least twice – as a memorial and in the construction of the church.“ (Hadjiev 2003:225). On lines 3 and 4 of the stone, a small depression is visible with an unclear purpose.</note></seg>
                </p> 
            </div>
